sections.ger:
Bezüglich des Bestehens und Nichtbestehens von <em>n</em> Sachverhalten gibt es $$\mathrm{K}_n = \displaystyle\sum_{
u = 0}^{n}  \dbinom{n}{
u}$$ Möglichkeiten.<br>Es können alle Kombinationen der Sachverhalte bestehen, die andern nicht bestehen.

sections.ogd:
With regard to the existence of <em>n</em> atomic facts there are $$\mathrm{K}_n = \displaystyle\sum_{
u = 0}^{n}  \dbinom{n}{
u}$$  possibilities.<br>It is possible for all combinations of atomic facts to exist, and the others not to exist.

sections.pmc:
For <em>n</em> states of affairs, there are $$\mathrm{K}_n = \displaystyle\sum_{
u = 0}^{n}  \dbinom{n}{
u}$$ possibilities of existence and non-existence.<br>Of these states of affairs any combination can exist and the remainder not exist.
